title: Ross Weir
text: Bought this thinking it was a UK company. They ship the boosters in from china and I go a Â£46.94 fee. The company didn't want to know and were just patronising on the support chat. I was going to send it back for a full refund, but guess what - you have to send back to china. So I guess I'll have to such it up. That will teach me for not doing my research. Hopefully this review will save someone else the pain.
